column5: The wife and I headed out last Sunday morning to try our luck at catching a few Small Mouth. Spent 4 hours catching and releasing numerous Smallies in the 14 to 16 inch range, plus way too many Northern's, most 30" or better and some nice size eating Walleye and few bigger ones as well. Beautiful calm morning.
Any pics of the pike??  Looks like you two had a good time!
Very nice Old Man. I'll be passing through Dinorwic on Sunday.
Nice catch !!!!! Weather looked perfect !!!!! Thanks for sharing .....
Just had 1600 paving stones delivered. So I know what I'm doing Sunday too   After this, I'm fishing the rest of the summer
Nice day of fishing but the price of 1600 stones is just to high.lol   Art
